</ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab>

    <lb n="1"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 1.350"><supplied reason="lost">Κλέωνι χαίρειν οἱ δεκάταρχοι τῶν λατόμω</supplied>ν</lem><rdg><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> χαίρει</supplied>ν</rdg></app> Ἀπολλώνιος ὁ διοικητὴς συνέτα<supplied reason="lost">ξεν </supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> Ἀρ</supplied>σινοείτηι νομῶι εργ<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> οὐκ ἔστιν οι<gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ἡμ</supplied>ῖν διδόναι τὸν σίδηρον ὡς καὶ φέρεται εξαλε 

    <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ογλεαντο ὡς αὐτοῖς ἐδόκει πρὸς ἐπὶ του 

    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> καὶ ἐλθόντων ἡμῶν ἐπὶ τὰ ἔργα συνετρι

    <lb n="6" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">βόμεθα </supplied><app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 8.277"><supplied reason="lost">δ</supplied>ανισάμενοι</lem><rdg><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>ωνισαμενοι</rdg></app> ἀργύριον κατακεχρήμεθα εἰς τὰ 

    <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>φ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ες ὅπως ἂν τὰ ἔργα συντέληται 

    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>στου. εἰλήφαμεν δὲ τοῦ ἀκαθάρτου καὶ τὸ 

    <lb n="9"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><unclear>εως</unclear> εἶναι τὸ διάφορον παρὰ τὰς <num value="4">δ</num> <expan><ex>δραχμὰς</ex></expan> δύο <num value="2"/> ὀβολοὶ

    <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> χρείαν γὰρ ἔχομεν <choice><reg>τρεῖς</reg><orig>τρῖς</orig></choice> <num value="3"/> τῆς ἡμέρας καὶ περι 

    <lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>εθα <choice><reg>ἵνα</reg><orig>εἵνα</orig></choice> <app type="editorial"><lem>ἔχωμεν<certainty match=".." locus="value"/></lem><rdg>ἕλωμεν</rdg></app> εἰς τὰ ἔργα σίδηρον ἀγοράσαι. 

    <lb n="12"/>εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab>

    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">Κλέα</supplied>ρχος Κλέωνι χαίρειν. ὑπογέγραφά σοι τῆς παρὰ <app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 1.350">Πετε<supplied reason="lost">χώνσιος</supplied></lem><rdg>Πετ<supplied reason="lost">εχῶντος</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">τοῦ ὑπαρ</supplied>χιτέκτονος ἐπιστολῆς <choice><reg>τὰ ἀντίγραφα</reg><orig>τἀντίγραφα</orig></choice>. πρὸς Διος οὖν καὶ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><unclear>σμου</unclear> διὰ τὴν <app type="editorial"><lem>ὑ<unclear>μ</unclear>ετέραν</lem><rdg>υ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ετεραν</rdg></app> ἁψιμα<supplied reason="lost">χ</supplied>ίαν <app type="editorial"><lem>ἐγὼ</lem><rdg>επ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/></rdg></app> ἐν <choice><reg>ἐγκλήμασιν</reg><orig>ἐγκλήμαισιν</orig></choice> γ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="4"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex>ἔτους</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>  

    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>πρ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ο παρὰ σοὶ ἔργα ἀποδ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ε<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>σφι<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἀπὸ δὲ Φιλαδελφείας ἕως <app type="editorial"><lem>Πατσώνθιος</lem><rdg>Παπώνθιος</rdg></app> πᾶσιν εγ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἡμέραν. καλῶς ἂν οὖν ποιήσαις ποιῶν τὰ προσο<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> τ</supplied>ῶν ἔργων <supplied reason="lost">ἐ</supplied>φʼ ὧν ἡμᾶς καταλείπει Ἀπολλώνιος <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost">ὁ διο</supplied>ικητὴς <unclear>ο</unclear></lem><rdg>ὁ διοικητὴς</rdg></app> <unclear>ο</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

